        "translation": "The sūtras are really their source.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b10_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故讚歎也。",
        "translation": "It's therefore praised.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b10_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b10_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上言人由經益。",
        "translation": "\"The above says that people are benefited by the sūtras.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b10_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則經有資成人義。",
        "translation": "The sūtras then have the meaning of nurturing adults.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b11_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故次歎也。",
        "translation": "Therefore, it's praised second.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b11_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶亮曰。",
        "translation": "Baoliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b11_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "海有八德。",
        "translation": "\"The ocean has eight virtues.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b11_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以譬經也。",
        "translation": "They're an analogy for the sūtras.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b12_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者因眾生之福海則漸深。",
        "translation": "One, the ocean of merit gradually becomes deeper because of the sentient beings who are endowed with it.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b12_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾生有感。",
        "translation": "All sentient beings have feelings.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b13_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以經教次第。",
        "translation": "That's why the sūtras teach a sequential approach.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b13_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從淺至深也。",
        "translation": "It progresses from shallow to deep.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b13_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二逐風而行。",
        "translation": "Second, they go from strength to strength according to the wind.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b13_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛菩薩。",
        "translation": "The buddhas and bodhisattvas.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b14_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨緣而化也。",
        "translation": "They transform people according to their conditions.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b14_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三河水入者。",
        "translation": "Three: He enters with the water of the river.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b14_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明涅槃納眾命之器也。",
        "translation": "This clarifies that nirvāṇa is a container for accepting all lives.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b15_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "下去類爾也。",
        "translation": "The following goes along with that.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b15_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "師子吼言世尊若言如來(至)云何獨令我受化身。",
        "translation": "Shizi roared, \"Bhagavān, if you say, 'Tathāgata,' why would you allow me to receive a transformation body alone?",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b16_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b17_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧亮曰。",
        "translation": "Sengliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b17_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第十歎佛也。",
        "translation": "\"The tenth is praising the Buddha.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b17_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以經典佛說理應歎也。",
        "translation": "According to the sūtras, the Buddha teaches the principle that praise is appropriate.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b17_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但說由慈生。",
        "translation": "However, it's said that it's produced from compassion.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b18_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故先問也。",
        "translation": "That's why he asked about it first.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b18_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶亮曰。",
        "translation": "Baoliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b18_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四生之中。",
        "translation": "\"Among the four kinds of birth, transformation birth is the most superior.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b18_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "化生最勝。",
        "translation": "The transformation birth is the most superior.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b19_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而佛為眾生。",
        "translation": "And the Buddha is a sentient being.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b19_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故胎生。",
        "translation": "Therefore, he's born in the womb.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b19_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "恩德之重。",
        "translation": "It's a great merit.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b19_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以致歎也。",
        "translation": "It's cause for praise.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b20_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時師子吼菩薩合掌長跪右膝著地以偈讚佛。",
        "translation": "At that point, the lion-roared bodhisattva joined his palms, knelt down with his right knee on the ground, and praised the Buddha in verse.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b21_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b22_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b22_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來是王化之主道被蒼生。",
        "translation": "\"The Tathāgata is the king, the lord of transformation, and the way is open to all sentient beings.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b22_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以最後興歎也。",
        "translation": "That's why he's the last to be praised.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b23_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來無量功德聚(至)能吼無量師子吼。",
        "translation": "\"The Tathāgata's innumerable merits are so great that he can roar the innumerable lion's roars.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b24_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b24_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧亮曰。",
        "translation": "Sengliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b24_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼國以偈為詠歌也。",
        "translation": "\"In that country, a verse is called a song.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b25_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "蓋盛德之至道也。",
        "translation": "It's called the ultimate path of prospering virtue.",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b25_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大般涅槃經集解卷第六十二",
        "translation": "Collection and Explanation of the Sutra of the Great Decease, Volume 62",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b26_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "弘安八年乙酉三月十日於西大寺寶塔院　為補闕書寫之畢　　　　唐人誠心",
        "translation": "Written to fill a vacancy at the jeweled stūpa of Xidaisi on the tenth day of the third month in the eighth year of Hong'an, by the Tang people, in good faith",
        "source": "T37n1763_062:0571b27_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    }
]